ed="T" n="0719b06"/><persName key="A001210">釋提雲般若</persName>，或云<persName key="A001210">提雲陀若那</persName>，<name>華</name>言<persName key="A001210">天智</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0719b07"/><placeName key="PL000000047983">于闐國</placeName>人也。學通大小，解兼真俗<ptr type="glossary" target="#g344"/>，呪術禪<lb
ed="T" n="0719b08"/>門，無不諳曉。<date from-iso="+0689-01-30" key="j19727421973066" to-iso="+0689-12-20"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0719002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>水</sic><corr>永</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0719002"/>昌</name>元年</date>，來屆于此，謁<persName key="A002099">天后</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0719b09"/>於<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛陽</placeName>，勅令就<placeName key="PL000000023665">魏國東寺</placeName>（後改<placeName key="PL000000023665">大周東寺</placeName>）翻譯。即<lb
ed="T" n="0719b10"/>以<date from-iso="+0689-01-30" key="j19727421973774" to-iso="+0691-11-28">其年己丑至<name>天授</name>二年辛卯</date>，出《華嚴經》<ptr target="#n117"/>、<lb
ed="T" n="0719b11"/>《法界無差別論》<ptr target="#n120"/>等六部七卷<ptr target="#n345"/>，沙門<persName key="A008996">處一</persName>筆受<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g53"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0719b12"/>沙門<persName key="A001192">復禮</persName>綴文，沙門<persName key="A002451">德感</persName>、<persName key="A008993">慧儼</persName>、<persName key="A008994">法明</persName>、<persName key="A008970">恒景</persName>等<lb
ed="T" n="0719b13"/>證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/><ptr target="#n346"/>。<persName key="A001210">智</persName>終年卒地，莫得而聞。</p>
